{"tid":200222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄：若半島爆發全面戰爭   中俄不會坐視不管","createTime":"2017-04-13T18:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T16:39:54.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b21491c345cbb3e57c2f6d431807e3a914652c8","tid":200222,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"《今日美國報》13日稱，目前的局勢非常具有戲劇性：美國航母正開赴朝鮮半島，而朝鮮威脅一旦遭到攻擊將核打擊美國本土。不過，美國朝鮮問題專家洛佩茲認為，對朝全面制裁的目標是讓平壤回到談判桌。而美國外交關系協會高級研究員施耐德擔心，是否有足夠的時間制定全面制裁措施，阻止朝鮮導彈到達美國本土，&ldquo;時間並非在美國這一邊。這樣，美國的選擇往往是極端的，除了談判，就是斬首或者動武&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯軍方13日表示，如果朝鮮半島爆發全面戰爭，中俄不會對在自己邊境地區發生戰爭坐視不管，會將美對朝的進攻視為對自己的直接威脅，「極有可能發起第二次抗美援朝。」"},{"pid":"754b5065c9f7f89dbdaba69a51c604f779a4661f","tid":200222,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"美俄對決again"},{"pid":"48e4ba941082b3dbb1e1d4792b3569bc21806063","tid":200222,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4ad54c39e0a61dfeca3536ee1ef355047348e0","tid":200222,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:49:19.000Z","msg":"中國變左夾心餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23e3bb599f66d42bfd31c2f1fed0bcc27c0d929","tid":200222,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:57:36.000Z","msg":"某強國想放棄美Trump份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f0a4c1ede13d8e39562c13172427233cbcdca2","tid":200222,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國變左夾心餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蛇頭鼠尾"},{"pid":"9b4635163aac640901cd2692c24ab085bb6b2487","tid":200222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"